title: Lawmaker wants state probe of Farmington apartment death
text: FARMINGTON, N.M. (AP) - A lawmaker wants the state Attorney General's Office to look into a Farmington apartment complex where a resident's death went unnoticed for weeks. The Daily Times in Farmington reported (http://bit.ly/1ZMu8Oa) Saturday that U.S. Rep. Ben Ray Lujan's office has asked Attorney General Hector Balderas to review ... ...
